The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for autonomous elevator button recognition, which falls under the scope of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The algorithm proposed in the paper also involves machine learning techniques such as Gaussian Mixture Model (GMM), which is a popular method in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques such as grid fitting and feature detection, which are also relevant to multimedia (cs.MM).
